ZH: 我們要在婚禮上送喜糖給每一個客人。
EN: We will give out wedding candies to every guest at the wedding.

ZH: 這包喜糖裡面有五顆。
EN: There are five candies inside this packet of wedding candies.

ZH: 妹妹的新婚喜糖都被人搶光了！
EN: Someone took away all the wedding candies of my sister's newlywed.

ZH: 這些喜糖太甜了，我只能吃一顆。
EN: These candies are too sweet, I can only eat one.

ZH: 我很喜歡這個新娘喜糖包裝的設計。
EN: I really like the packaging design of this bride's wedding candies.

ZH: 這些喜糖都是手工做的，特別有紀念意義。
EN: These wedding candies are all handmade, which makes them especially meaningful.

ZH: 我們要在公司慶功宴上送喜糖給所有的同事。
EN: We will give out celebration candies to all our colleagues at the company's celebration dinner.

ZH: 在喜糖裡面藏了獎品，讓嘉賓們去抽獎。
EN: We hid prizes inside the wedding candies for the guests to draw.

ZH: 給喜糖包裝上面寫上新郎新娘的名字和結婚日期。
EN: Write the names of the bride and groom and the wedding date on the packaging of the wedding candies.

ZH: 喜糖包裝上的絲帶顏色要和婚禮的主題色相呼應。
EN: The color of the ribbon on the wedding candy packaging should match the theme color of the wedding.

ZH: 收到新婚喜糖，我們祝福他們永遠幸福快樂。
EN: After receiving the wedding candies, we wish them eternal happiness.

ZH: 我們特別訂製了一款獨特的喜糖包裝。
EN: We specially customized a unique packaging for the wedding candies.

ZH: 喜糖代表著新婚的情意和祝福。
EN: Wedding candies symbolize the affection and blessings of the newlyweds.

ZH: 每一顆喜糖都象徵著新婚的甜蜜回憶。
EN: Each wedding candy symbolizes the sweet memories of the wedding.

ZH: 喜糖是中國婚禮傳統文化的一部分。
EN: Wedding candies are part of the traditional Chinese wedding culture.

ZH: 我們的喜糖有個獨特的口味，大家都讚不絕口。
EN: Our wedding candies have a unique flavor that everyone praises.

ZH: 每一個客人離開婚禮時，我們都會給他們一包喜糖作為紀念。
EN: We will give each guest a packet of wedding candies as a souvenir when they leave the wedding.

ZH: 這個婚禮的喜糖很有創意，每一顆都像一個小禮物。
EN: The wedding candies at this wedding are very creative, each one is like a small gift.

ZH: 能收到喜糖是我們對新婚夫妻的祝福和心意。
EN: Receiving wedding candies is our blessing and goodwill towards the newlyweds.

ZH: 我們準備了一桌子的喜糖供客人品嘗。
EN: We prepared a table full of wedding candies for the guests to taste.
